products will vanish.

00:43:22.060 --> 00:43:24.220
So if I only write the
pieces that don't vanish,

00:43:24.220 --> 00:43:29.140
then I only have four
pieces, which are these four.

00:43:57.040 --> 00:44:00.790
So all other combinations
that I didn't write

00:44:00.790 --> 00:44:03.205
vanish, and those four survive.

00:44:09.880 --> 00:44:12.880
We'll do one example,
so you see what

00:44:12.880 --> 00:44:15.880
the strategy is for getting
