00:46:29.750 --> 00:46:31.760
So now, I'm going to
do one thing, which

00:46:31.760 --> 00:46:34.850
is going to end up simplifying
our lives a little bit later

00:46:34.850 --> 00:46:35.647
on.

00:46:35.647 --> 00:46:37.730
And I'm going to use the
fact that, when we talked

00:46:37.730 --> 00:46:40.550
about production
of quarks, we said

00:46:40.550 --> 00:46:42.500
we're going to produce
this Cn type of quark

00:46:42.500 --> 00:46:44.510
and not the phi n bar
bar type of quark.

00:46:48.370 --> 00:46:54.780
So phi n bar,
remember, corresponded

00:46:54.780 --> 00:46:56.630
to sub-leading
spinner components.

00:47:02.170 --> 00:47:04.500
So let's just decree
