00:50:55.300 --> 00:50:56.140
they just cancel.

00:51:02.333 --> 00:51:04.000
So there was two terms
in the Lagrangian

00:51:04.000 --> 00:51:06.036
that had psi n bar bar.

00:51:10.000 --> 00:51:37.930
And the remaining
