00:51:41.620 --> 00:51:45.470
OK, so this is Lagrangian that's
just in terms of the Cn field.

00:51:45.470 --> 00:51:47.020
We'll call it double star.

00:51:51.096 --> 00:51:52.810
Previous guy was
